com.veil.extendedscripts.extendedapi.constants

Interface IColorCodes


  • public interface IColorCodes
    This object stores colors available to all scripting handlers through the "Key" keyword. The values stored here are the characters for each color without the formatting character.

      • getValue

        char getValue(java.lang.String name)
        Gets the color code character for a given color name.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the color as a string (e.g., "Red") not case sensitive.
        Returns:
        The corresponding color code character, or 'x' if not found.
